{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "story_surfer_set_1", "eventName": "顶峰之景", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕间", "storyName": "顶峰之景", "storyInfo": "完成任务踏上归途的寻澜，突然离开队友行动，独自走入军工企业的大楼。她的目标简单明确，却造成了意料之外的混乱......", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wild_m", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，这趟任务可算是结束了。", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "训练的时候虽然针对长距离行动专门练过体能，但和实际出任务真的没法比啊。", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再多跑一小时我的腿可能就要报警咯。你呢，蒂拉，你还好吗？", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佣兵在下午的阳光中伸了个懒腰，然后停下脚步，回头看向离自己只有几步路远的队友。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "札拉克女孩似乎有些心事，一边走一边频频向四周环视，但在听到同伴声音的那一刻，她马上温柔地笑了起来。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我感觉挺好的，可能是因为平时我也会自己去野外走很远吧。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真有你的，就算是例行的侦察任务，强度也不是闹着玩的，你还能额外留出精力来。", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒也不至于啦，顺利完成任务就好。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对了，午间口粮里的那块糖果是你放的吧？", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，之前我听你在聊天的时候提到过，你一直都很喜欢吃甜食。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上午的探察结束之后，休息时适当补充糖分能一定程度缓解疲劳，之后的行动会更轻松。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我就带了一块给你。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的多谢你啦。", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没事没事，在外执行任务其实会遇到很多训练里没有接触过的东西，一旦遭遇突发情况又会很危险。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帮助别人是我应该做的，不如说我还做得不够多。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#2$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还好今天的活提前干完啦，蒂拉你回去后准备怎么放松，看看电影？还是做些什么别的？", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂拉并没有很快回应，而是若有所思地看向遥远的地平线，像是在看着荒野边缘几栋高层建筑的轮廓。"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......我不知道......", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#9$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她说话的声音小了下去，但下一瞬间她像是忽然想起什么一样睁大了双眼。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对了！", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#6$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“对了”？还有什么事吗？", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的队友有些摸不着头脑，疑惑地挠着头。"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思，你一个人先回本舰吧，报告我之后回去做。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想到一个事情，一定要先去看一看，很快就能做完。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我们的任务不是已经——", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦！我懂了！不用多解释，你快去吧。", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，而且我得赶时间，等一会就没机会了，之后回本舰再见！", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#3$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "run1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "run1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当老板的得力助手也不容易呀，除了日常任务还要接额外的活。", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过......我没记错的话，那边不是那个军工企业的园区吗？", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们和那边又扯上什么关系了？", "name": "黑钢先遣队员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佣兵的视野里只剩下了日落前的空旷景色，他望向远方的办公大楼，不解地眨了眨眼。"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_uptown_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=2>沃尔沃特科钦斯基旗下某工业园区，主办公楼外</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_medium", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_207"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停下。", "name": "安保人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你没有身穿带有标识的标准制服，是访客的话就出示预约证明，否则禁止进入。", "name": "安保人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大楼门口，安保人员拦住了一位自顾自地往里走的札拉克少女。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好，能不能通融一下呢？", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是来看看，去一趟上面就离开，不会在这里久留。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_207"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "外来人员没有预约证明，不能进入办公楼。", "name": "安保人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......我不能提供什么证明，但我需要上去一趟。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#9$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有必要的话，我的武器和装备都可以留在这里作为担保。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对我来说这件事很重要，能不能麻烦你让我上去呢？", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安保人员上下打量了一番来客，原本紧绷着的身体似乎稍稍放松了一些。"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_207"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......情报人员？", "name": "安保人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对，黑钢先遣小组。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_207"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要去高层？", "name": "安保人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没错。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "听到少女的回答，安保人员明显舒了一口气，接着他向一侧移开一步，让出前进的路。"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_207"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上去吧。记住武器保持收起，远离办公区域，我会知会内部人员和你交接。", "name": "安保人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通行时间最长一个小时，严守规定。", "name": "安保人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "谢谢，我很快就下来。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "run2"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "run2", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_207"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小声）高层的那群人不知道又在盘算什么怪事情......", "name": "安保人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小声）每次都搞得神秘兮兮的，接头线人进来也不让留下记录......", "name": "安保人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安保人员用余光目送札拉克少女走进正门，自顾自地摇了摇头。"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_motorroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沃尔沃特科钦斯基办公大楼内，除了数据存储机的低声嗡鸣，还有快速响起的脚步声在无人的楼层间回荡着。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "run3"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "run3", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "札拉克少女在这些楼层一刻都没有停留，只是一味地走向通往更高层的楼梯。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "电梯在到达十五层之前就停止运行了，她不得不穿过一整层工作区，挤开面带讶异的人群，跑进楼梯间继续向上走。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要能赶在结束之前走上去的话——"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小姐！请你......停一下！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一个西装革履的身影气喘吁吁地挡在她面前，他弯腰撑着扶手，连喘几口气后才直起身。"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......听我说两句好吗？", "name": "管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管你来这里的目的是什么，都不能再往上走了。", "name": "管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上面是严禁外部人员出入的区域，你已经破坏了访客规定了，我得请你离开。", "name": "管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我还要到上面去看一看，只到这里是看不到想看的东西的。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#11$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放宽心，对你们公司的事务我一点都不关心，你们做了什么事情我也不在乎。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我上去之后马上就会离开。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "说着她就准备继续向上走，眼前身着西装的人赶忙伸出一只手臂拦住她的去路。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小姐，我知道你是带着任务来的，但我不能放任你继续调查我们公司了。", "name": "管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "调查？你在说什么？", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#11$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要去的是楼顶，那里什么都没有。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你还想去上层的核心区？", "name": "管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不可能的小姐，你在离开访客区域的那一刻就触发警报了。", "name": "管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当时我们只能紧急停止客梯运行，没想到你还一路往核心区走。", "name": "管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，重申一次，我没有任何东西要调查。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "急着上楼的少女再一次迈出脚步，但这一次对方不是伸出一只手了，而是用整个身子堵住楼梯。"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再走一步，我就通知整栋大楼的警备，你就别想从这里全身而退了。", "name": "管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家都不想把事情闹得太难看，在事态升级之前请你快点离开这里——", "name": "管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "run4"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "run4", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站在台阶上方的男人还没有来得及说完话，札拉克少女就已经敏捷地翻过了楼梯扶手。"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一眨眼之间，她就已经大跨步向高层走去，楼梯间里留下一句带着回声的回应。"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思，再拖下去就真的看不到了，有什么话留到之后再说！", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......看不到？什么看不到？", "name": "管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管理人员呆呆地看着少女消失的方向，数秒后他才反应过来，而后举起了手中的通讯器。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老板，紧急情况，麻烦您来处理一下！", "name": "管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1259_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_indoor_3", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "run5"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "run5", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂拉几乎是一步三级地朝更高楼层走去。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "与有人工作的楼层不同，楼梯间外传来的声音越来越小，她感觉到了，自己离楼顶的距离也越来越近。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又上了一层楼后，她看到了楼梯的终点，和那扇通向楼顶的门。但同时她也看到，另一个人已在门口等待着。"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小姐，我是这里的负责人之一。", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的调查行动在公司内部造成了不小的混乱，也造成了很多误会。您和我做一次最终谈判，解决这个问题怎么样？", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂拉放慢脚步走到高管面前，她能看到那只撑着手杖的手在不断颤抖。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您好，先生。误会就是，我不是来调查的，也没有任何任务。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事到如今，何必遮遮掩掩呢？", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你是克里夫的亲信，我这里虽然只是沃尔沃特科钦斯基的一家分公司，不过，一点点话语权也还是有的。", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信不管是我们还是黑钢，都希望事态平息吧。", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "说着，沃尔沃特科钦斯基的代表人伸出右手做出一个手势。"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告诉我克里夫对你吩咐了什么，我们可以为你提供——", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的行动与克里夫先生无关。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哈，是我想简单了。", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，事情就是很单纯。我就只是去你们的楼顶一趟，我不会做任何有损你们利益的事情，之后我会立刻离开。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#2$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然，您可以自己想一想，我能在楼顶看到什么机密信息？", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "带着不可告人的目的跑到这儿来的是你！我要是能猜到克里夫要什么，直接跟他打电话不就结了！", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你当我是第一天面对你们这种情报人员吗？", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不如您现在就给他打个电话如何？", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "别耍花招了——", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我没时间和您解释了，先生。再拖下去，我想看的美景就彻底看不到了。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您要是执意不相信，不如和我一起走上楼顶看看。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我会让您亲自见证，我们之间的误会到底有多大。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“美景”？哼，看来这是什么黑钢内部的暗语了？这次行动的名字叫什么？“美景行动”？", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......看来是彻彻底底说不通啊。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#2$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虽然让您这样一个满脑子商战的人跟在身边多少有点煞风景，但您看这样如何？", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您把路让开，让我上去，在此期间，您可以一直监视我，如果我有什么出格的举动，可以立刻将我驱逐出去。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我要你现在就——", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......这场交易可还没成立呢，先生。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#8$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高管紧盯着蒂拉的眼睛，试图权衡放眼前这个人上天台和得罪克里夫究竟哪个更加糟糕。"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最终，他稍稍让出了半个身位。"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我答应你的条件，但我会盯紧你，别想从这里带走任何一点东西！", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心好了，先生。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就看好了。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂拉走向通往楼顶的门，伸手将它推开。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_door"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "47_g15_eveningglow_L1/47_g15_eveningglow_R1/47_g15_eveningglow_L2/47_g15_eveningglow_R2", "solidwidth": "1280/1280/1280/1280", "solidheight": "720/720/720/720", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 60.0, "yFrom": 360.0, "yTo": 720.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黄昏时分，空旷的楼顶上流动的清风吹过蒂拉的面颊。"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天的夕阳与平时看起来不同，在有些朦胧的天空中，光芒从云层的各个缝隙间散射而出。"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而那些橙红色的光芒，形成无数道各有间隔的光柱，点亮云底和半边暗色的天空。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂拉站在门口看向天地交界线上的光芒，然后如释重负般地叹了口气。"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真好......", "name": "寻澜"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这是......什么？", "name": "高级管理人员"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夕阳，但不是普通的夕阳，也许很多年都只能看到一次这样的景象。", "name": "寻澜"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有在沙尘天气结束后放晴的下午，加上完美的能见度，再配合天边合适的云形......", "name": "寻澜"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有条件都得到满足，才能让阳光在空中散射成如此美妙的样子。", "name": "寻澜"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虽然上来的路并不顺利，但能看到这样稀少的景色，一切都是值得的。", "name": "寻澜"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高管望着天边闪耀夺目的阳光束，他难以掩饰脸上的复杂表情。"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g13_rooftop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就这些？你不去找找别的东西？", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就看看天就完事了？", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "为什么要做别的事情呢？", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她慢步走向金属防护网，高管在她身后怔怔立着，一步都跨不出去。"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起这栋大楼里的人和事，现在这片美景对我来说才是有意义的。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "观赏它的地点和时间都必须刚刚好，而我找到了对的地点。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您看，在你们急着找不存在的问题和答案的时候，景色又变了。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#3$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂拉伸出手，指向西方的地平线，高管也不由自主地顺着她的指引看向天边。"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太阳已经落下，但余晖依然在云间留下美妙而夺目的光芒，像是明亮的火焰从地平线下升腾而起。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "时间正好，位置也和我想象中的一样，这里真的是附近最好的观景地。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到这栋楼的那一眼我就感觉到了，只有从楼顶的角度才能看到，这难得一见的景色。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "无论你们误解我想做什么，我唯一的想法，自始至终就只有看到这片美景而已。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#2$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，我在这里要做的事情都做完了，您现在明白我的目的了吗？", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这......可是......", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂拉看了看依然无法接受现状的高管，耸了耸肩。"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您同意的话，我现在可以离开这里了吗？", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "高级管理人员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1257_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "谢谢您的理解。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#10$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本舰，先遣小组蒂拉呼叫，请求人员支援以便返回。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高管在逐渐暗下的天色中看着蒂拉完成通话，然后任凭她从自己的身边走向门口。"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很快，刚才动人心弦的景色就消失不见，楼顶上只剩下孑然站立的一个人。"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g9_modernoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂拉，说明情况。", "name": "“桥夹”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑钢的老板拉开椅子坐了下来，他看向站在桌边的蒂拉，少女的表情很是平静。"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在回本舰的路上，我看到那栋楼的时候，就突然想到那里的楼顶应该有绝佳的观景角度。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天恰好任务完成得比较顺利，在日落之前就结束了，加上天气也很完美——", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以就想上去看看，毕竟见到那种稀少景色的机会实在太难得了。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#5$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是在问你这个。", "name": "“桥夹”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#2$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天下午你造成的混乱你自己也知道。沃尔沃特科钦斯基从分公司到总公司不断给我打电话。", "name": "“桥夹”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#6$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非常抱歉！", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#5$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#7$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那种夕照散射的样子只要条件稍有变化就会消失，只有在特定的时间登上楼顶才有机会看到。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#7$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那样的夕景，即便想要寻找也很难遇到第二次了......", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#2$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里夫皱起眉头看着自己的助手，但很快他脸上凝重的表情就缓和了下来。"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老板，要是没别的事的话，我就......", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#5$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "“桥夹”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#2$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里夫先生，那个——", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#9$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你已经放松过了，正巧现在有个很棘手的任务，需要一个得力的人手。任务概要在这儿，你可以自己看。", "name": "“桥夹”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "单人潜入任务，基本上全程在地下通道里完成。没有夕阳，没有森林，甚至没有天然洞穴......", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#6$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老板，这算是对我的报复吗？", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#5$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他能完成任务的人碰巧都不在，仅此而已。", "name": "“桥夹”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "见札拉克没有推脱的意思，克里夫冲她点了点头，径自离开了办公室。"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "难得一见的夕阳景色，换一次既无聊又危险的潜入任务......勉勉强强说得过去吧。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#2$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且克里夫先生这次居然没扣我的假期，难道他今天心情其实不错？", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#3$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......算了，与其去猜克里夫先生高兴还是不高兴，还不如老老实实照他说的做呢。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1040_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走啦。", "name": "寻澜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1040_1#3$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}